snippet.title: Game Showcase - Sonic Robo Blast 1
snippet.description:
Hello, today we feature a very...special fangame of Sonic.

This was one of the very first sonic fangames that came out back then.

unfortunately the game glitched on me at the second stage's boss. oh well.

leave a comment or w/e.

-WW
